examples.en: There are approximately 8,000 species of ants.
We had to fumigate our apartment to get rid of the ants.
She lifted up the rock and found ants crawling underneath.
The way ants work is an object lesson in order and organization.
Ants have considerable powers of intercommunication by means of their antennae.
In desperation, we called in an exterminator because the house was infested with ants.
